1. Required ingredients - Maida, sugar, yeast, pizza toppings
2. Take a luke warm water and add yeast and suagr, give some time to activate the yeast
3. mix the yeast with maida and kneed a dow
4. leave 2 hours for rest
5. take a dow and make your own shapes according to your needs
6. Add a pizza toppings and cheese on top of shaped pizza dow
7. bake the pizza in a oven
8. leave for 40-50min in oven 
9. take uout a pizza and enjoy!
